title: Rounded Condensed Font
content:
Hello,

I am looking for this font used on one Qantas' logojets

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317140205im_/http:/typophile.com/files/turf_6397.jpg)

I had a feeling it might be Helvetica Rounded Condensed. But the O simply doesn't look right, the W is off too. Same goes for Anchor. Any other ideas, input?

Thanks for any help!

C.

Font: 

 Brauer Neue
